Not guilty.

1174
01:02:24.950 --> 01:02:27.786
- Number three?
- Guilty.

1175
01:02:28.787 --> 01:02:30.331
Number four?

1176
01:02:31.832 --> 01:02:33.626
Guilty.

1177
01:02:33.709 --> 01:02:36.462
- Number five?
- Not guilty.

1178
01:02:37.546 --> 01:02:40.841
- Number six?
- Not guilty.

1179
01:02:41.842 --> 01:02:43.510
Number seven?

1180
01:02:43.594 --> 01:02:45.304
Guilty.

1181
01:02:45.387 --> 01:02:47.431
